A boondii bɔŋaŋ ibuŋgaa , mi puaapilɛnɔɔ nyuna ya te I yeema pɛ mi dimi yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ .
Miŋ kua o tandaa niŋ , nduyɛ mbo ke ya yaula pɔmbɔlaŋ lapum a Masale Mɛlɛkaleŋ okɔɔ .
Mi ndepilɛnɔɔ loŋ ndoo pɛɛku naa chuaambuaa Baabuiyo a yauwo hoo “ The Harp of God . ”
Mi yaa dimi yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ chiɛiyo a chiɛiyo ya pilɛ kpe .
Mi puaapilɛnɔɔ simi nɛɛso ndɔɔ , okoŋ , mbo dimul la le miŋ chal o yɔmndo choo .
Mbo dimi aa , “ Nɛɛ ke yɛ num dioo le wanaa cho chuiŋnda wa kɔɔsaa ?
Ŋ waŋnuŋ a kɔl kɛndɛ le waŋnda yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ dimullo nduyɛ miŋ mal Chɛhowa kɔɔsɔɔ o ba . ”
Mi puaapilɛnɔ kaasoŋnɔ cheleŋ pɛɛku ya maa le nyaaloo sɔlaa o waŋnda yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ dimullo niŋ , ŋ nɔ miŋ biunuŋ teleŋndaŋ lapum .
Mɛɛ wɔsilaŋ la hiou okoŋ kɔɔli , mbo sɔla fandaa le biunɔŋ ndɔɔ . Mi laa ndɔ simnuŋ Chɛhowɛinɔɔ nduyɛ mbo yiŋ .
Mɛɛ chɔuwo chuu , mi dimi yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ le wɔsioŋ ŋmuuŋ o lɛŋnde Aililaŋ ndeŋ niŋ baluaŋndo .
Ŋ sina mɛɛ kpɛ simlachinɔ lekaŋndo ndoo nɔ kpaayaa yɛ le .
Ŋ wa a kɔl kɛndɛ tau kanifuule , yaa kue wɔ o dɛndɛ kua o mɛŋndaŋ choo wo niŋ te .
Miŋ dimi yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ le wɔsilaŋ la ŋuɛɛnu o lɛŋii doolɛ mɛŋndaŋ ma balu keŋnde niŋ , naa Chɛhowɛiyaa ve le wa .
Misiɔnaliiyaa kua a dɛndɔɔ wa cho o dɛndɔɔ Sibiaa niŋ ( chɔŋ o bamiallo choo mbo kua o bakɛndɔɔ choo ) : Loŋ Pakiŋ , Dik Luai , Kɔsiti Maki , a Staŋle Kata
Lɔɔlɔɔ mi ndaa ke naa suwaa nyuluaa , piyalaŋ , a tiɔɔŋ .
I wa bɔɔ suɛi kɔndɔfili le chɔɔ waŋnda hunɔɔ .
Hau , mialla kua bɔɔ o lɛŋii mɛŋndaŋ ma balu keŋnde niŋ .
Mɛɛ naŋ fuuluu , mi komal Masiŋ Bɔɛi nduyɛ mi kaala ndu . Ndepilɛnɔ Misiɔnaliinɔ ndoo naŋ tau wo o wa ni .
Nduyɛ mi dimuluŋ yapila aa , ‘ Lonadi , te a yeema pɛ chuaambɔɔ hoo , a nɔ ma keŋela chɔ chɔ . ’
Mɛɛ lɔɔlaŋ la hiou la yaa mi dimul ndu , nduyɛ o lɔɔla ŋɔmpum kɔɔli , miŋ chal o nɔɔ niŋ .
Ma viam ya naa Masiŋ misiɔnaliileŋ o Puɛɛto Liko niŋ . I kue lɛ o dɛndɛ sɛnɛi naŋ sɔla wo niŋ te .
Le tamaseliiyo , o sɔndɔkɔlɔ nɔ diolaŋ aa Potala Pastilo niŋndo , yuŋgula Seiyaa Chɛhowaa wa loŋ latiɔɔŋ a chuauwa tau .
Mi dimul chuaambɔ pɔmbɔɔ diolaŋ Hilda , te o yeema pɛ kɔlaŋ yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ dimioo a naa latulu .
Miŋ pindul ndu kɔwɛilaŋ , nduyɛ miŋ kua yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ dimioo latulu .
O wa niŋ toosiaŋndo le kɔlaŋ o naa nda vem ndu le yooŋgu kɛndɔɔ dimioo o lɛŋnde Ikueedɔ leŋ niŋnda . Mbo dimi aa , “ La loonuŋ lɛ ya le , nɛɛ ?
