Nyɛ Ebilaham tosa wo ndu tosa ni mi Mɛlɛka siiŋguu ndu wana sakpo . Ndu yɔnuŋ ni maa chua o chua po ndɔɔ Aisaki le mbo soli ndu maa sala o maaŋndo choo wo .
