( Pitɛ Tasoo 1 : 8 ) Mi Chemisi dimul puaapiliaa nduaa pɔyaŋnda aa , “ Wanaa cho a tambɛi waŋnda o hɔl chieeŋ naŋ nda , nda Mɛlɛka hɛli le ma wa wanaa nɔ tiindaŋ o Masanɔɔ Chiisu Kiliti niŋ tau tau wa ni .
